headline: Activist investors make Wall Street 'efficient': Starboard CEO

Smith sits down with Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi to discuss what drew him to activist investing, how he selects investment targets, the Kenvue (KVUE) and Kimberly-Clark (KMB) deal, and more. For full interviews, highlights, and key insights, check out more from Yahoo Finance Invest.
